  "detailed_description": "One day, three buddies decided to rob a bank.<br>But something went wrong and the cops showed up...<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1576740/extras/dae1182fbbfcbfc7cad6ee2dace7d727.poster.avif?t=1761155469\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1576740/extras/dae1182fbbfcbfc7cad6ee2dace7d727.webm?t=1761155469\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1576740/extras/dae1182fbbfcbfc7cad6ee2dace7d727.mp4?t=1761155469\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Now, these feisty felons need to smarten up and make the most incredible jailbreak.<br>Find the way to freedom while hiding from the guards, searching for key cards to open the locked doors, and avoiding dangerous pitfalls!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1576740/extras/53644f880c677f3ad74c33e08e10a0d9.poster.avif?t=1761155469\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1576740/extras/53644f880c677f3ad74c33e08e10a0d9.webm?t=1761155469\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1576740/extras/53644f880c677f3ad74c33e08e10a0d9.mp4?t=1761155469\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Complete 60 levels, and get out of prison at any cost!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1576740/extras/d60b6e67d088b13bde6d1b5dad62e4f4.poster.avif?t=1761155469\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_